To support the release of this album, Furay formed an alliance with David Geffen and Asylum Records.
He toured as an opening act for America and Linda Ronstadt during 2006.
In 2007, he toured with a new formation of the Richie Furay Band.
The Richie Furay band continued to tour through 2008 and 2009.

Paul Richard Furay (born May 9, 1944) is an American singer, songwriter, and Rock & Roll Hall of Fame member.
